title: Blueface & Sharp Interview 10 Girls & Things Go Left!!!
description:
The new season of the Blue Girls Club just wrapped, but Sharp sat down with them to catch the tea before the finale. 
-----
00:00 Intro
0:15 https://www.instagram.com/prolificrip... | https://www.instagram.com/officialnov... | https://www.instagram.com/kaylamfkn.b...
8:32 “Nubian” was on season 2 and now she's back to get her spot
9:08 Sharp asks if she pays rent for her to call it her house
10:08 Sharp tells Nova that she should've polished her appearance to come on the podcast
11:26 Sharp brings Fiesty to squash the beef with Nova
18:44 Nova is salty because Fiesty stole 14$ from her
24:34 Nova is furious because she says Fiesty talked recklessly about her kid
28:06 https://www.instagram.com/iamxbbg/ | https://www.instagram.com/itsnastysavay/ | https://www.instagram.com/la.juicy_ho...
35:50 Savay building a dog shelter, social media will bring income, meanwhile she got her IG deleted so many times
56:16 https://www.instagram.com/annaclutch_/ | https://www.instagram.com/imarraa.elon/ | https://www.instagram.com/drakotheedon/
57:49 Santana aka Leo, says being in the house is like jail
1:02:30 Sharp says Drako looks like she has an attitude, her face
1:03:08 Drako says she's a stripper, she wants to be a video vixen, that's the goal
1:07:18 Drako has her own opinion but Sharp is not having it
1:07:40 Drako says she made $300 so far, Sharp gets mad saying that's cheap labor 
1:09:07 Drako claps back at Sharp: "I don't care about your opinion"
1:17:50 Leo made $800 without posting anything on her OF at all, Sharp makes fun of her
1:18:09 Drako is irritated because Sharp talks down on Leo for making $800
1:20:03 Sharp calls them goofy, Imarraa defends them
1:21:33 Imarraa says Sharp keeps coming for them, for what? He says it's because of Drako's face
1:22:35 Sharp is fuming, the girls clap back, Sharp gets in their faces then leaves the pod
-----
